Class Chunk

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.Chunk
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CodeChunk, DocChunk
    public class Chunk
extends java.lang.Object
    A document "chunk". Chunks start on a particular line number (numbering from 1), and contain specified contents.
